data.Answer:
the following documents are considered valid id if they include the voter's current name and residence address: utility bill
 tax statement
 military identification
 college or university fee card or student identification
 lease agreement
 income tax statement
 vehicle registration;
 mortgage statement;
 preprinted check or bank deposit slip;
 mail addressed to the voter at their current address;
 a sworn statement from a voter in the precinct;
 bank statement/credit card statement.
